Sample file:

```
int f1(a1);
int f1(a1);
```

press `A<backspace>{<CR><ESC>` on the first line, you get:

```
int f1(a1){

}
int f1(a1);
```

`2j.` will make it:

```
int f1(a1){

}

int f1(a1);
```

That is, the only modification done by `.` is the added empty line on the second last line of the file.

